{"tid":1403362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「好人一生平安」：多謝今日係尖沙咀送6200豬嘴既香港媽媽","createTime":"2019-08-03T18:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T11:19:48.000Z","uid":251631,"like":96,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ccec2f8dc8ad74c8ff1cdf2988f8e695864ce3b5","tid":1403362,"uid":251631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:39:49.000Z","msg":"今日發夢去左K11門口幫手搬路障<br />\n搬搬下有位師奶拎住一大袋6200豬嘴<br />\n問我地要唔要<br />\n見到入面起碼有20個以上既高級野<br />\n全部都裝好曬d filter<br />\n即刻可以用<br />\n又叫我地散出去比其他無gear既手足<br />\n見到呢幕真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前線學生哥食餐飯都覺得貴<br />\n未必咁有財力買到咁多裝備<br />\n真係好多謝呢位香港媽媽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FyF0ujR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFyF0ujR.jpg&h=e8be96a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/acri0ry.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Facri0ry.jpg&h=11043811&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n都想同其他出唔到力既人士講<br />\n如果自己出唔到力，可以出錢課金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買裝又或者課比立場、星火一樣都可以幫到呢場運動架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">光復香港，時代革命</div></span></span></strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</div></span></strong></span><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"91000cb67d4c12d2321ac3fc248929417fa18a86","tid":1403362,"uid":267235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85962986bd92ea80c641277db